#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_text_image
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Deliver flowers to live up to your dedication for your loved ones."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ສົ່ງມອບດອກໄມ້ເພື່ອສະແດງເຖິງຄວາມຕັ້ງໃຈຂອງທ່ານທີ່ມີຕໍ່ຄົນທີ່ທ່ານຮັກ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"A small shop with a very large selection of roses. Nice prices and above all"
" a very professional and friendly welcome."
msgstr ""
"ຮ້ານຂະໜາດນ້ອຍທີ່ມີດອກກຸຫຼາບໃຫ້ເລືອກຫຼາຍ. ລາຄາດີ ແລະ ສິ່ງສຳຄັນທີ່ສຸດແມ່ນການຕ້ອນຮັບທີ່ເປັນກັນເອງ ແລະ ເປັ"
"ນມືອາຊີບ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"A wide range of high quality products and a warm welcome! I recommend this "
"shop 200%!"
msgstr ""
"ສິນຄ້າຄຸນນະພາບສູງຫຼາກຫຼາຍລາຍການ ແລະ ການຕ້ອນຮັບທີ່ອົບອຸ່ນ! ຂ້ອຍຂໍແນະນຳຮ້ານນີ້ 200% ເລີຍ!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"As we use local growers, our flowers last longer and smell better. Just like"
" the event you want to celebrate with flowers!"
msgstr ""
"ເນື່ອງຈາກພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ດອກໄມ້ຈາກຜູ້ປູກໃນທ້ອງຖິ່ນ, ດອກໄມ້ຂອງພວກເຮົາຈຶ່ງສົດໄດ້ດົນກວ່າ ແລະ ມີກິ່ນຫອມກວ່າ. ເ"
"ໝາະສົມທີ່ສຸດສຳລັບງານທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສະເຫຼີມສະຫຼອງດ້ວຍດອກໄມ້!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid "Bio Flowers"
msgstr "ດອກໄມ້ອໍແກນິກ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Don't offer pesticides to your beloved one! By choosing our flowers, we "
"guarantee you organic flowers."
msgstr ""
"ຢ່າເອົາສານພິດໃຫ້ຄົນທີ່ທ່ານຮັກ! ເມື່ອເລືອກດອກໄມ້ຂອງພວກເຮົາ, ພວກເຮົາຮັບປະກັນວ່າເປັນດອກໄມ້ອໍແກນິກ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid "Eco-Friendly Packaging"
msgstr "ການຫຸ້ມຫໍ່ທີ່ເປັນມິດກັບສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text
msgid ""
"From your local producer to your door, discover how we deliver our multiple "
"sorts of flowers and bring you happiness."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກຜູ້ຜະລິດທ້ອງຖິ່ນເຖິງໜ້າບ້ານທ່ານ, ຄົ້ນຫາວິທີທີ່ພວກເຮົາຈັດສົ່ງດອກໄມ້ຫຼາກຫຼາຍຊະນິດ ແລະ ມອບຄວາມສຸກໃຫ້ກັບທ່"
"ານ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_cover
msgid "Live life in full bloom"
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຊີວິດໃຫ້ເບີກບານຄືດອກໄມ້ທີ່ເບັ່ງບານ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid "Local Producers"
msgstr "ຜູ້ຜະລິດພາຍໃນທ້ອງຖິ່ນ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_text_image
msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr "ພັນທະກິດຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text
msgid "The Orchid Concept"
msgstr "ແນວຄິດແບບດອກກ້ວຍໄມ້ (The Orchid Concept)"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_orchid.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "ເຄື່ອງມືຊ່ວຍຈັດການທີມ (Theme Utils)"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_call_to_action
msgid "There are always flowers <br/>for those who want to see them."
msgstr "ມີດອກໄມ້ສະເໝີ <br/>ສຳລັບຜູ້ທີ່ຢາກຈະເຫັນພວກມັນ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_text_image
msgid ""
"To do so, we collaborate with local producers who care about the environment"
" and cultivate their flowers with love."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຮ່ວມມືກັບຜູ້ຜະລິດທ້ອງຖິ່ນທີ່ໃສ່ໃຈສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ ແລະ ປູກດອກໄມ້ດ້ວຍຄວາມຮັກ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_quotes_carousel
msgid ""
"Very nice, colorful shop with many choices in the heart of a very pretty "
"town."
msgstr ""
"ຮ້ານທີ່ສວຍງາມ ແລະ ມີສີສັນຫຼາກຫຼາຍ ພ້ອມກັບຕົວເລືອກມາກມາຍ ຕັ້ງຢູ່ໃຈກາງເມືອງທີ່ໜ້າຮັກ."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"We use 100% recycled materials. We believe the best gifts should also do "
"good for the planet."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ວັດສະດຸຣີໄຊເຄິນ 100%. ພວກເຮົາເຊື່ອວ່າຂອງຂວັນທີ່ດີທີ່ສຸດຄວນຈະດີຕໍ່ໂລກນຳ."

